description:
$2,800 per month. Luxury apartment available for rent on Boston.com's "Most Desirable Street in South Boston." On East Broadway in between H and I. #9 bus route right out front, #7 two blocks away. Two blocks from Stats/Lincoln and one block from the Playwright - this is the ideal location. Views out the back windows of the Boston city skyline and only a few blocks from the beach and Castle Island. This apartment is right on the St. Patrick's Day Parade route. Marble countertops, stainless steel appliances, in unit washer/dryer, dishwasher, and central air conditioning. Unit available on September 1st.
Great landlord.  No realtors please.  Listing not approved to be relisted by anyone other than property owner.

Tenant responsible for gas and electric.
